transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Ji very good evening sir. Lokeshwar ji baat kar rahe hain?
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Ye main sir Uzair baat kar raha hun IndiaMART se aapke account manager. Abhi sir aapka ek concern raise hua tha aapne shayad customer care pe baat kiya tha.
Customer: Haan sir bolie sir.
Executive: Ji to kya issue aa raha hai sir kis regarding aapne ye concern raise kiya tha?
Customer: Kya?
Executive: Product add karwane the aapko?
Customer: Na na na.
Executive: Mujhe ye customer se mera baat hua tha.
Customer: Ji.
Customer: T T L bolke cosmetics ka kuch details chahiye tha Pune walon ka.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Unse baat hua tha mera.
Executive: Achcha to matlab IndiaMART se aapko kya chahiye main ye nahi samjha.
Customer: Main IndiaMART se T T L International bolkar Delhi mein ek company hai unse baat karna chahta hun.
Executive: Ek minute ek minute line pe rahiye.
Executive: Aapne kya buylead consume ki thi?
Customer: Sir?
Executive: Iski buylead consume ki thi jis company ka aap naam le rahe hain?
Customer: Nahi nahi nahi nahi mujhe kuch product chahiye tha unse isliye call kiya.
Executive: Call kijiye ga sir.
Executive: Nahi aap Abhay Enterprise se baat kar rahe hain na?
Customer: Haan sir main Abhay Enterprise se hi baat kar raha hun mujhe wo T T L International hai na.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: New Delhi ka.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Haan unka unka mujhe kuch product chahiye tha isliye main unko maine call kiya.
Executive: Nahi nahi to uske liye to aap Google pe search kariye.
Customer: Hum jo karate hain.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer wants to connect with TTL International.



Resolution:

- Executive suggested searching on Google.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, product details, google search
